FT  03 SEP 93 / People: Constructive careers
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Clive Drinkwater (below left), formerly chairman and md of JS Bloor
(Newbury), has been appointed md of PERSIMMON HOMES (Wessex) in succession
