FT  03 SEP 93 / Order on Elstree Studios weighed
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
HERTSMERE Borough Council has decided to consider placing a compulsory
purchase order on the historic Elstree Studios in Hertfordshire.
This would reduce the value of the 15.5-acre site to make it more tempting
for film-makers. Its owner Brent Walker, the property and leisure group,
wants to sell it to developers.
