FT  02 SEP 93 / UK Company News: English &amp; Overseas recovery
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
ENGLISH &amp; Overseas Properties returned pre-tax profits amounting to Pounds
12,000 for the six months ended June 30 1993.
