FT  02 SEP 93 / UK Company News: Calderburn falls as forecast but expects
upturn
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Calderburn, the office furniture group, reported pre-tax profits of Pounds
1.41m for the first half of 1993, a 36 per cent fall on the comparable
