FT  02 SEP 93 / UK Company News: Multitrust net asset value rises to 48.6p
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Net asset value per share of Multitrust increased from 33.2p to 48.6p over
the 12 months to June 30. At end-December 1992 the value was 35.25p.
