<HEADLINE>
FT  01 SEP 93 / World News in Brief: Algerian executions
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Algeria executed seven Moslem fundamentalists convicted of involvement in a
bomb attack last year at Algiers airport in which nine people died. Among
those executed was a pilot with the state airline.
